+# Why CVE-2026-3449 Is Not Applicable to @tootallnate/once@1.1.2 and Requires No Patching
+
+This document explains why **CVE-2026-3449** is **not applicable** to **@tootallnate/once@1.1.2**, and confirms that the vulnerable code path **does not exist** in that release, making patching or backporting for this version unnecessary.
