+## Root Republish Notes
+
+This dummy patch exists for **audit and build metadata only**. It adds this document via the Root patch pipeline so that:
+
+- CVE-2026-3449 remains tracked in `meta.json`
+- The patch step completes without modifying once runtime code
+- Auditors have an on-record explanation of why no functional change was applied
+
+For projects that actually use `once()` with `{ signal }`, upgrade to **@tootallnate/once@3.0.1+** or apply the functional hook patch on **2.0.0 – 3.0.0**.
+
